name: Gan 14 Maglev
description: Experience the pinnacle of speed cubing with the GAN 14 MagLev. This revolutionary 3x3 boasts magnetic levitation technology, creating effortless rotations and unmatched smoothness. Dive into a world of 1296 customizable settings, tailoring the feel to your every whim. Push your limits with superior corner-cutting and unwavering stability, shattering your personal bests. Lightweight and ergonomic, the GAN 14 MagLev is a masterpiece of engineering, crafted for champions and aspiring speedsters alike. Unleash your potential. Conquer the cube. Elevate with the GAN 14 MagLev.

name: Gan 251 M
description: The GAN 251 M is a lightning-fast 2x2 speed cube built for performance. It's ultra-lightweight (under 60g!), boasts powerful magnets for snappy turns, and boasts extensive tuning options to customize the feel to your exact preference.

name: MoYu MF8826 MeiLong
description: The MoYu MeiLong 4x4 is a budget-friendly speed cube that is perfect for beginner and intermediate cubers. It has a smooth turning mechanism and accurate corner cutting, making it a great choice for anyone who wants to improve their solving times.
